{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina, Slovakia, offers stunning views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout is ideal for those seeking a high-quality living experience with ample storage space and natural light. The apartment features an east-facing living room with kitchen, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The bedroom is north-facing, preventing overheating and eliminating the need for air conditioning in summer months. The bathroom has a bidet shower by the toilet, underfloor electric heating, and a washing machine/dryer. The apartment is equipped with high-quality materials and features a timeless stone sink and mirror with LED lighting. The hallways are designed to maximize space utilization and provide ample storage. The kitchen includes built-in appliances, including an induction hob, BOSCH dishwasher, and oven. The bathroom has a spacious brick shower enclosure with a storage ledge and a sliding kitchen table for workspace while cooking or dining."}
